{"tid":2142605,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《John Wick》系列導演 參與重拍元斌《殺手代父》 ","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T14:18:31.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"525e20bbae8a663474fae900c6e3afbd0226886f","tid":2142605,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"自從《上流寄生族》於奧斯卡大勝而回，韓國電影就大受荷里活注目，而其實早幾年已經有荷里活公司買下韓國電影嘅重製版權，例如New Line就買下由元斌主演嘅2016年韓國電影《殺手代父 (아저씨)》嘅版權，並搵黎《John Wick》創作組合製作。<br />\n<br />\n《殺手代父》係由李楨凡執導嘅動作劇情電影，講述元斌飾演嘅神秘孤僻當鋪老闆，為咗拯救被黑社會虜走嘅鄰居小女孩素美 (金賽綸飾) 而重出江湖嘅故事，當年為韓國全年票房冠軍。而重製版就搵黎《John Wick》系列導演Chad Stahelski及編劇Derek Kolstad參與製作，韓國娛樂鉅頭CJ E&amp;M亦係製作方之一。據報製作方非常滿意Derek Kolstad撰寫嘅劇本，並開始尋找適合嘅導演人選，但Chad Stahelski相信不會為此片執導。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/8/6/7f9ad1d92b6c124237f5de141e5c43b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F8%2F6%2F7f9ad1d92b6c124237f5de141e5c43b8.jpg&h=e561884d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=24434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dhobby%26aid%3D24434&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOopVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=d853906f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=24434</a>"},{"pid":"b59696ff5b96e0db17eb2d4b8ded950b3ad97106","tid":2142605,"uid":19990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"即係《大叔》呢套野正呀，同John wick 一樣打得好正， 韓國動作片之中最好嗰堆係經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bc2ab3e90a2947f229699d64cc493154574c6a","tid":2142605,"uid":19990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"咩2016年 大叔唔係2010年咩？"},{"pid":"886c0346e11d6f65f35e62b7ce152e674f24b6bc","tid":2142605,"